OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry, bright and warm on Friday but
OL,7,Fcloudier with the chance of a shower
OL,8,Flater. Cooler and cloudier over the
OL,9,Fweekend with a chance of showers.
